[Course_Description]
Get tips, tricks, and valuable insights in this series on project management. Instructor Cole Mercer addresses key skills and trending topics that product managers need to know to maximize their time, energy, and focus. Learn why you have to get out of the office and talk to users, what to do to develop the PM mindset, and how to structure a product management or project management team. Plus, learn the difference between agile, lean, scrum, and Kanban, and the roles of product manager, product owner, and project manager. Cole also provides tips for collaborating better with stakeholders, hiring and managing product managers, and leading productive meetings.